  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201403/ba77783eda2141fe8c2eec85b4405fd2.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>光影巡游&mdash;&mdash;真爱每一天</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t时间：2月25日（星期二） 19:00 - 20:00<br />\n\t主讲老师：Eileen老师（<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/lin2/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师沪江部落&gt;&gt;</a>）<br />\n\t公开课地点：英语大厅（<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk</a>）</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #a52a2a;\"><strong>名师档案：</strong></span></p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" height=\"33\" width=\"445\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201403/45b623d730294d95892d87136a4b3f6e.jpg\" /></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">小艾老师（Eileen）<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t沪江网校留学方向老师，北京外国语大学硕士，主讲雅思写作；托福口语、写作；同时在英语大厅开设公开课&ldquo;小艾老师带你光影巡游&rdquo;。</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/lin2/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">戳此直达老师部落主页&gt;&gt;<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t</a></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #a52a2a;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>视频回顾：</strong></span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">【课程大纲】</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">What would you do if you could travel to the past and make some changes?</span><br />\n\t<strong>1.影片赏析</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>2.台词讲解</strong><br />\n\t-That's very sweet of you.It's just a shame you left it till the last night.You should have tried creeping along the corridor while we still had time.<br />\n\t-Okay,the&quot;last night&quot;was a bad idea?<br />\n\t-Very bad idea,it feels like an ever so slightly insulting afterthought.&quot;last night&quot;was never going to work.<br />\n\t-All right.Good.I've got it.<br />\n\t-Wow.I tell you what.Why don't we see how the summer goes and then you ask me again on my last night?<br />\n\t-Your last night？<br />\n\t-Yes.Try me on the last night.See what happens then,shall we?It's exciting.<br />\n\t-Right.<br />\n\t-No,it's a perfect plan.That's absolutely perfect.Last night.<br />\n\tAll the time travel in the world can't make someone love you.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>3.文化贴士</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t想提前一周知道最精彩的公开课安排吗？那就来订阅沪江CCTalk电子报吧！<strong><a href=\"http://app.hujiang.com/mail/sub/72/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">电子报的订阅入口&gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t沪江网校还为大家提供了其他的活动，欢迎大家预约：<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/app/event\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>最新活动预约</strong></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201209/58f013100fe44857a846c5c5aef19325.gif\" style=\"width: 377px; height: 15px;\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>请注意！参与本活动须使用沪江全新语音学习软件CCTalk，使用指南如下：</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1.<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bulo.hjenglish.com/n1/?source=eng2009\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">注册</span></a></strong>沪江网获得用户名（已是沪江用户的不必注册）；<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_gkkyd\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/fdac82641c98410a9fb1352dcdff5cd3.jpg\" /></a><br />\n\t2. 点击网址<a href=\"http://class.yeshj.com/zt/cctalk\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(7, 93, 179);\">http://class.yeshj.com/zt/cctalk</span></a>下载CCtalk软件；<br />\n\t3. 软件安装结束后，输入沪江网的<b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\">用户名</span></b>和<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\"><b>密码</b></span>登陆CCtalk；<br />\n\t4. 点击下图中用红圈标注的&ldquo;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\">语音教室</span></strong>&rdquo;；</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201403/7c63e75b1299439e98181526b371bf1b.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span s